##### Remap the player icon #####

?:[EQU $RACE Noldor]
monster:<player>:0x8D:0x80
?:[EQU $RACE Sindar]
monster:<player>:0x8D:0x90
?:[EQU $RACE Naugrim]
monster:<player>:0x8E:0x80
?:[EQU $RACE Edain]
monster:<player>:0x8E:0x90
